      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白素贞"
      ],
      "text": "儿就该奏明圣上，搭救为娘，才是道理。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002020_e00038",
      "play_id": "01002020",
      "scene_id": "01002020_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许仕林"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿上殿连奏数本，圣上不准也是枉然。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002020_e00039",
      "play_id": "01002020",
      "scene_id": "01002020_s02",
